---
title: Southeast Asian Salt & Pepper Beef with Garlic Rice, Peanuts & Aioli
description: Watch out salt and pepper squid, because our beef version is going to steal even your biggest fans! With all the umami, but pan-fried instead of deep-fried, this is a quick and easy dinner that's going to blow your mind.

